s2517: Eighth year: Zi Jiu came fleeing, along with Guan Zhong they avoided the Wu Zhi disorder.
s2518: Twelfth year: Wu Zhi killed the ruler and established himself.
s2523: Wei Hui Gong Shuo returned to enter. Fourteenth year.

s2534: Qi Huan Gong Xiao Bai first year, spring: Qi killed Wu Zhi.
s2549: Tenth year: Qi attacked us, because of Jiu.
s2553: Sixth year: Xi Fu Ren, Chen woman, passed through Cai; Cai was disrespectful to her, she hated them. Chu attacked Cai, captured Ai Hou and returned.
s2557: Eleventh year: Chu captured our hou.
s2565: Eleventh year: Zang Wen Zhong condoled Song's flood.
s2570: Ninth year: Song great flood, the duke blamed himself. Lu sent Zang Wen Zhong to condole.
s2586: Tenth year: Wan killed the ruler; Qiu Mu had righteousness.
s2597: Thirteenth year: Cao Mo hijacked Huan Gong. Returned the lost territory.
s2598: Fifth year: assembled with Lu people at Ke.
s2602: Song Huan Gong Yu Shuo first year: Zhuang Gong's son.
s2630: Seventh year: began hegemony, assembled the feudal lords at Juan.
s2631: Twenty-eighth year: Qu Wo Wu Gong extinguished Jin Hou Min, offered the treasures to Zhou; Zhou commanded Wu Gong to be Jin's ruler, and combined their territories.
s2639: Zheng Li Gong first year: Li Gong fled and after 17 years returned to enter.
s2647: Jin Wu Gong established and combined Jin; already established 38 years, did not change the yuan, continued from his first year.
s2648: Twentieth year: buried at Yong, first used human sacrifices to follow in death.
s2649: Twelfth year: attacked Deng and extinguished it.
s2655: Second year: the feudal lords attacked us.
s2663: Thirty-ninth year: Wu Gong died; son Gui Zhu established, as Xian Gong.
s2664: Qin De Gong first year: Wu Gong's younger brother.
s2680: Second year: first made the Fu sacrifice, sacrificed to the She altar, split dogs at the four gates of the city.
s2692: Second year: Yan and Wei attacked the king; the king fled to Wen, established Zi Yi.
s2698: Seventh year: took a Wei woman. Wen Gong's younger brother.
s2704: Sixteenth year: attacked the king; the king fled to Wen, established Zi Yi.
s2720: Seventeenth year: Zheng seized our Zhong Fu.
s2724: Fourth year: executed Yi, entered Hui Wang.
s2735: Seventh year: rescued Zhou's disorder, entered the king.
s2740: Fifth year: the crown prince's mother died early. Hui Hou gave birth to Shu Dai.
s2742: Fourteenth year: Chen Wan came fleeing from Chen, Tian Chang began from this.
s2743: Fifth year: attacked the Li Rong, obtained Ji.
s2744: Fourth year: built the Mi altar.
s2745: Fifth year: younger brother Yun killed Du Ao and established himself.
s2748: Twenty-first year: Li Gong's son Wan fled to Qi.
s2757: Twenty-third year: the duke went to Qi to observe the She sacrifice.
s2791: Eighth year: completely killed the former Jin Hou's various sons.
s2807: Ninth year: began building Jiang capital city.
s2820: Tenth year: granted Qi Hou the mandate.
s2855: Twelfth year: Crown Prince Shen resided at Qu Wo, Chong Er resided at Pu City, Yi Wu resided at Qu. Because of Li Ji.
s2886: Twenty-third year: attacked the Shan Rong, for Yan's sake.
s2901: Thirty-second year: Zhuang Gong's younger brother Shu Ya was poisoned to death. Qing Fu assassinated Zi Ban. Ji You fled to Chen, established Min Gong.
s2919: Sixteenth year: extinguished Wei, Geng, Huo. First enfeoffed Zhao Su at Geng, Bi Wan at Wei, began from this.
s2933: Second year: Qing Fu killed Min Gong. Ji You from Chen established Shen as Xi Gong. Killed Qing Fu.
s2935: Seventeenth year: Shen Sheng was general; the noblemen knew he would be discarded.
s2939: Di attacked us. The duke was fond of cranes; the soldiers did not fight, extinguished our state. The state resented it; Hui Gong created disorder, extinguished his descendants, instead established Qian Mou's younger brother. Wei Dai Gong first year.
s2949: Lu Xi Gong Shen first year: Ai Jiang's mourning came from Qi.
s2950: Twenty-seventh year: killed younger sister Lu Zhuang Gong's consort, because of licentiousness.
s2955: Wei Wen Gong Hui first year: Dai Gong's younger brother.
